         <item>
            <title>Version 1.40</title>
              <description>
                <![CDATA[
                  <html>
                    <head>
                      <style type="text/css">
                        body {
                          font-size: 9pt;
                        }
                      </style>
                    </head>
                    <body>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Emulator window now displays name of running machine in the title bar</li>
                        <li>QuickSave/QuickLoad last saved state - Press Option+Command+S and Option+Command+L to re-save and re-load last loaded state</li>
                        <li>Status bar LED's for Power, Pause, Ren-Sha Turbo (Joystick auto-fire), Caps Lock, Code/International key, Cassette I/O, Floppy Disk Drive I/O</li>
                        <li>Ren-Sha Turbo slider for the status bar</li>
                        <li>Improved machine selector, with filtering by Install status, Family and Search</li>
                        <li>Latest version of blueMSX emulation core</li>
                        <li>Bug fixes, minor UI improvements!</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p><a href="https://github.com/melllvar/CocoaMSX/releases/v1.40">Full list of changes</a></p>
                    </body>
