         <item>
            <title>Version 1.2</title>
              <description>
                <![CDATA[
                  <html>
                    <head>
                      <style type="text/css">
                        body {
                          font-size: 9pt;
                        }
                      </style>
                    </head>
                    <body>
                      <ul>
                        <li>Removed the black side borders from the main emulator window</li>
                        <li>Improved mouse support (press Cmd+Click to disengage mouse mode), as well as new mouse configuration options</li>
                        <li>Option to enable/disable status bar (now off by default)</li>
                        <li>Improved machine selector - now on a separate tab in Preferences. Download, install and uninstall machines automatically. Special thanks to the blueMSX team for providing server hosting</li>
                        <li>Improvements to the keyboard editor, including automatic layout detection and more intelligent key editing</li>
                        <li>Limited gameplay capture and recording</li>
                        <li>Mixer configuration options - control volume and balance of all six channels</li>
                        <li>Ability to paste text into the MSX computer (by simulating keystrokes)</li>
                        <li>Lots of bug fixes</li>
                      </ul>
                    </body>
                  </html>
                ]]>
              </description>
